	(87,'2.1','Always change vendor-supplied defaults and remove ...','Always change vendor-supplied defaults and remove or disable unnecessary default accountsbeforeinstalling a system on the network. This applies to ALL default passwords; including but not limited to those used by operating systems; software that provides security services; application and system accounts; point-of-sale (POS) terminals; payment applications; Simple Network Management Protocol (SNMP) community strings; etc.).','NA',66,1,4,'2017-04-10 13:56:03','2017-04-10 13:56:03'),
