	(89,'2.2','Develop configuration standards for all system com...','Develop configuration standards for all system components. Assure that these standards address all known security vulnerabilities and are consistent with industry-accepted system hardening standards.Sources of industry-accepted system hardening standards may include; but are not limited to: • Center for Internet Security (CIS) • International Organization for Standardization (ISO) • SysAdmin Audit Network Security (SANS) Institute • National Institute of Standards Technology (NIST).','NA',66,1,4,'2017-04-10 13:56:03','2017-04-10 13:56:03'),
